type Head<T extends unknown[]> =
  T extends [infer U, ...unknown[]]
  ? U
  : never

type Tail<T extends unknown[]> =
  T extends [unknown, ...infer U]
  ? U
  : []

type HasTail<T extends unknown[]> =
  T extends [] | [unknown]
  ? false
  : true
